Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.08,0:10:27.05,Title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(700,460)\fsp8\b1}芽间
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.91,0:01:46.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好烫 好烫
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.18,0:01:49.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别慌 芽间
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.42,0:01:56.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.00,0:02:06.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 大家请吃
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.10,0:02:10.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她叫你们吃呢 以一副很自负的表情
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.07,0:02:14.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 我感觉有点凉
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.80,0:02:16.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别这样好吗 我很难受
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.53,0:02:17.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请吃哦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.32,0:02:21.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鸣笛个子很高 随意吃最大的一个
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.83,0:02:22.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.59,0:02:25.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她说 因为你个头最高
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.42,0:02:32.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 你说的没错 我真的变得很壮啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.30,0:02:37.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吃 很好吃啊 芽间
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.90,0:02:38.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.82,0:02:39.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.35,0:02:43.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你给我的是什么的第一呢 芽间
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.86,0:02:47.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给雪集葡萄干最多的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.88,0:02:49.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可没这么说
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.65,0:02:53.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,芽间 我希望直接由你告诉我
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.03,0:02:56.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请你告诉我 芽间
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.22,0:02:58.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪集
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.35,0:03:04.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了 纸和笔  给 让她写在上面
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.72,0:03:11.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个嘛 怎么写不出来 仁坦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.48,0:03:13.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么呢 明明日记上能写出来的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.28,0:03:15.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让我试试
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.19,0:03:19.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么回事 也不是没有水啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.90,0:03:21.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再来一次 再让我来一次
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.81,0:03:23.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等 等一下啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.75,0:03:26.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鹤子 我很难受
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.67,0:03:28.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鹤子
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.38,0:03:35.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知为何我现在好困
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.61,0:03:38.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 感觉乏力了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.61,0:03:41.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这是怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.97,0:03:47.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,芽间没有生我们的气 她原谅了我们
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.51,0:03:51.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁知道有没有原谅我们呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.77,0:03:57.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是 如果生气的话 不会给我们做蒸面包吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.84,0:04:02.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果是因为没有原谅我们 为了责备我们而出现呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.00,0:04:11.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说 既然她能写字 一开始就应该写给我们
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.69,0:04:16.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说的也是 这样的话就能和我们对话 我们也就相信了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.37,0:04:20.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁坦和芽间也有点笨啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.87,0:04:27.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是 说是让我们相信芽间的存在 其实是为了独自占有
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.61,0:04:32.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,久川 安城 打工的钱要好好存着哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.48,0:04:39.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一定会做出烟花的 一定会让芽间成佛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.17,0:04:41.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪集
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.20,0:04:51.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么活蹦乱跳肯定会累的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.39,0:04:59.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们打算一起制作烟花 为了 
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.26,0:05:02.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让你成佛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.97,0:05:08.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你会感到高兴吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.26,0:05:20.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你还醒着
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.07,0:05:21.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你 仁坦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.41,0:05:25.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.06,0:05:33.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样就好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.14,0:05:47.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样就好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.13,0:05:49.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,求求您了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.75,0:05:57.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然不行吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.53,0:05:58.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,转圈圈
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.69,0:06:01.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,芽间 跑太快的话会跌倒的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.17,0:06:04.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,芽间在跑吗 那我也来
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.20,0:06:06.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,站住 芽间
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.36,0:06:07.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来这边呀
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.90,0:06:09.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.39,0:06:17.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能原谅那个喜欢仁坦的我
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.71,0:06:23.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然 我还是对他
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.99,0:06:26.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能放弃 对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.32,0:06:31.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.26,0:06:35.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下周的工作安排 能不能和我换一下
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.07,0:06:37.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,工作
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.88,0:06:40.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,周四桥那边有工地活
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.37,0:06:42.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那边的薪水较高 所以想去那边
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.77,0:06:44.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁坦 
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.49,0:06:46.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,终于玩腻了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.67,0:06:49.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我给你说哦 那边有
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.50,0:06:56.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.17,0:06:59.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.55,0:07:06.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了 是她 是芽衣子的母亲联系山叔的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.09,0:07:08.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然是阿姨吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.95,0:07:12.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那 叔叔并不反对烟花这件事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.95,0:07:22.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙仍然活在过去
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.31,0:07:28.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,芽衣子发生了那样的事 之后时间就没再走过
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.30,0:07:36.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想让她回到现在 所以不希望让她再回想起来
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.92,0:07:37.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.44,0:07:43.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托您了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.55,0:07:44.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.18,0:07:45.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,松雪
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.44,0:07:49.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可能我没有达到阿姨那种程度 但是我能理解她的感受
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.34,0:07:54.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我喜欢着你的女儿 喜欢着芽衣子
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.08,0:08:00.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想为了芽衣子做一些什么 因为我也生活在过去
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.05,0:08:02.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正因为如此 我要
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.84,0:08:14.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没想到你会做那么磋的事 吓我一跳
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.16,0:08:16.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也吓了一跳
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.78,0:08:18.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真是不变啊 雪集
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.43,0:08:22.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了芽间 你什么都肯做
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.14,0:08:23.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鹤子
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.40,0:08:31.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样可以吗 既然你相信了 还让芽间成佛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.28,0:08:34.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明那么执着于芽间
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.72,0:08:38.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,通过宅太 我们依然可以对话 可你却
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.87,0:08:40.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那得通过宅太
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.04,0:08:47.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好啊 辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.00,0:08:50.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宅太 现在去打工吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.15,0:08:52.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今晚会弄到很晚 
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.93,0:08:55.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以先回去一趟 送芽间回去
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.29,0:08:59.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,芽间在那里吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.62,0:09:04.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知为何 她不想呆在家里 去哪都要跟着我
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.18,0:09:08.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 我想和大家一起努力
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.49,0:09:11.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的 好的 她说想和大家在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.79,0:09:17.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,芽间 你头发还是那么长吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.04,0:09:19.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪集
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.05,0:09:25.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 话说 这家伙成长得和我们一样
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.62,0:09:27.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成长了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.88,0:09:29.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 到底是为什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.66,0:09:33.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是美女吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.47,0:09:36.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在说什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.82,0:09:40.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁 谁会喜欢这种丑八怪
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.48,0:09:48.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,差不多勉强算是美女吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.56,0:09:50.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说 是可爱型吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.96,0:09:53.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么叫勉强算是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.60,0:09:54.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吵死了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.50,0:09:55.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁坦 你这个大笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.09,0:09:58.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吵死了 笨蛋 你就是勉勉强强
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.07,0:10:05.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感觉像是在看演戏
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.13,0:10:10.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但并不是那样 因为
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.11,0:10:17.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪集坏掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.42,0:10:29.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.60,0:10:31.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 给你们做
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.55,0:10:35.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,烟花 烟花
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.34,0:10:37.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了 太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.23,0:10:40.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不能让你们干火药的活儿
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.17,0:10:43.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过要不要帮忙一些简单点的操作
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.31,0:10:43.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.32,0:10:46.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁坦 太好了哦 
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.82,0:10:54.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叔叔 拜托您了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.17,0:10:57.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托您了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.90,0:11:04.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你吓人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.16,0:11:05.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.51,0:11:09.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个会从竹筒里飞出来
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.51,0:11:12.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我觉得红色多一点的会可爱一些
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.87,0:11:14.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可爱
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.10,0:11:18.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你内心和外表相差好大啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.47,0:11:22.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后从这里点燃
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.40,0:11:24.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来如此 那这边呢 
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.72,0:11:30.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这只是个装饰 只为了便于搬运
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.88,0:11:34.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厉害啊好厉害 好厉害啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.72,0:11:35.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁坦 听我说
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.04,0:11:38.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,芽间 危险啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.12,0:11:41.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别松手啊 仁坦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.15,0:11:42.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,芽间
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.52,0:11:46.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鸣笛 做好了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.73,0:11:49.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在跳到你背上了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.06,0:11:53.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的吗 芽间小姐 饶了我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.02,0:11:56.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鸣笛 鸣 鸣鸣鸣笛
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.79,0:12:03.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,芽间 明明看不见却看得见
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.14,0:12:15.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看得见 我赢不了她 以前也是现在也是 都赢不了她
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.82,0:12:19.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.30,0:12:23.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去买点饮料
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.13,0:12:41.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.92,0:12:44.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多亏你了 
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.11,0:12:50.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多亏你跑了 不然我也快叫出来了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.29,0:12:51.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪集
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.65,0:12:55.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,芽间就在身边 这个我已经认了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.44,0:13:01.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是芽间却看不见 也说不了话
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.33,0:13:05.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我曾希望再一次见到芽间
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.14,0:13:08.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可为什么只有宅太
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.64,0:13:14.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然对她而言只有宅太 宅太也只有芽间
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.22,0:13:16.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和那时一模一样
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.39,0:13:22.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你放弃了吗 明明开始叫他仁坦了 却又变回宅太了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.43,0:13:27.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这种什么都知道似的态度是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.07,0:13:32.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我能看穿的也只有你 算是同类人的共鸣吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.80,0:13:36.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才不要和你这种性格恶劣的人一样
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.38,0:13:37.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冷静点
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.31,0:13:48.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我错了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.38,0:13:57.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪集
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.40,0:13:59.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我错了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.85,0:14:16.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之前说的那件事 我挺认真的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.75,0:14:18.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之前
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.05,0:14:21.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们要不要交往试试
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.62,0:14:28.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真的对男人没有任何耐性啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.09,0:14:30.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别开玩笑
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.49,0:14:31.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,漂亮的中段踢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.69,0:14:35.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说你啊 什么漂亮的中段踢啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.36,0:14:39.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笑什么笑 我刚才真的很吃惊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.65,0:14:40.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有那么吃惊吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.19,0:14:45.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是这里了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.02,0:14:48.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 斗志上来了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.06,0:14:53.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁坦 安鸣的娃娃不见了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.94,0:14:56.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,安鸣回家了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.66,0:15:01.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 突然间就回去了 真是只随性的小猫啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.28,0:15:05.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果芽间真的在仁坦那儿 
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.27,0:15:09.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,实现愿望之后她不就要消失了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.64,0:15:13.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了 仁坦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.62,0:15:17.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没什么 到打工时间了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.56,0:15:18.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么早就要走了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.73,0:15:20.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,芽间 你打算怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.00,0:15:22.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要和鸣笛在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.54,0:15:24.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她说想呆在这里 可以吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.76,0:15:26.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.60,0:15:32.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然可以啊 尽情呆着吧 一直呆个够吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.86,0:15:35.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你太闹了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.66,0:15:37.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为我很高兴啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.73,0:15:44.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,芽间果然还是感到高兴吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.65,0:15:46.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然还是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.48,0:15:49.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看那个了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.81,0:15:50.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冬季校服
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.03,0:15:52.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女高中生用双节棍战斗的那个
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.66,0:15:54.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你终于看了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.03,0:15:58.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最初我觉得她是夏日的禽兽
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.51,0:16:02.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.78,0:16:05.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经穿起冬季校服了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.43,0:16:16.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,写好了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.26,0:16:17.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,芽间 你在吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.76,0:16:18.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.51,0:16:26.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.90,0:16:29.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厉害 你好厉害啊 芽间
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.23,0:16:34.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是家里的本子写不了 为什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.02,0:16:35.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再多写几句
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.44,0:16:37.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们多聊聊吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.02,0:16:39.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好啊 聊什么
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.22,0:16:42.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个嘛 让我想想
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.59,0:16:53.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那天 你那个时候 对我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.96,0:17:01.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没什么 对了 要不要接龙
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.76,0:17:02.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,画图接龙
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.85,0:17:03.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要玩
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.87,0:17:05.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.61,0:17:10.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你那个是什么 好像烧饼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.97,0:17:19.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大书包 蓝宝石 玻璃球 马里奥 小手
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.44,0:17:25.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把小手和在一起 就是幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.05,0:17:37.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,带上望远镜 芽间队员开始搜索任务
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.19,0:17:55.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.63,0:18:06.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,芽间
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.02,0:18:12.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您拨打的电话暂时无法接通
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.02,0:18:13.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶 打不通
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.19,0:18:15.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经在打工了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.12,0:18:18.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我为什么在着急 
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.65,0:18:25.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我为什么在奔跑
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.74,0:18:30.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,芽间应该在秘密基地
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.71,0:18:36.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可我却 为什么如此
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.75,0:18:44.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁坦 来这边 
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.39,0:18:53.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁坦 芽间她
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.55,0:19:06.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不要 我不要让芽间消失
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.35,0:19:13.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁坦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.06,0:19:30.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁坦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.23,0:19:39.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不要 我绝对绝对不要仁坦死掉
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.63,0:19:47.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在说什么呢 你不也死了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.65,0:19:49.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.42,0:19:54.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,芽间你真古怪
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.30,0:19:57.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说别人古怪的人就在说自己
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.92,0:19:59.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 好 我们走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.32,0:20:01.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.83,0:20:02.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鲤鱼
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.07,0:20:03.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鲤鱼
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.91,0:20:10.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,河里有一条很大的 我想在近处看看
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.71,0:20:13.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看 在那里 在树根那儿
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.90,0:20:15.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,模糊的发白的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.41,0:20:16.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.91,0:20:20.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.56,0:20:34.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁坦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.86,0:20:38.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好疼啊 仁坦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.50,0:20:41.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁坦 你喜欢撒娇吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.84,0:20:46.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直 一直呆在这儿吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.99,0:20:49.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁坦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.11,0:20:53.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你呆在这 我帮你把它抓来
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.18,0:20:57.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁坦 会湿的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.33,0:20:59.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁坦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.68,0:21:05.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 笨蛋仁坦 你会感冒的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.19,0:21:22.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快回来吧 仁坦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.04,0:22:58.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的很感谢你 仁坦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
